{
  "stem": "11998.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when the Nazis came to get her, instead of being-- instead of going with them, she went and she jumped out the window.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she, of course, killed herself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But that was, that was the-- if the Nazis came for you, the Gestapo came for you, your life was pretty well over, whether they interrogated you or they thought that you had some information.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so they-- we knew we were living in a very hostile environment.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And people generally did not take it lightly to go outside of the, the boundaries or to take off the Star of David.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, of course, [? and the police. ?]",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was Polish police that was sort of traffic cops.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the German soldiers were very, very visible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Gestapo was very visible in-- on all the main streets and, you know, patrols going through in the evenings and--",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not that I know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I, I'm sure that that happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we heard-- I heard about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I, I don't know of first-hand knowledge.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, in 1942, we went to  Srodula.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes. '41 we were in the open ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in-- to Srodula, we went in the spring.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I remember the, the mud on the streets of the villages was terrible.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And before that, of course, we had the people from Oswiecim or Auschwitz come to Sosnowiec.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A lot of them came to Sosnowiec and Bedzin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had to absorb them in our district.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then in '40-- in '42--",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
